@definition: 1 ch × 10 ch = 4840 sq yd = 1⁄640 sq mi
@description: Acre is area unit, symbol: [ac]. Definition of 1 acre ≡ 1 ch × 10 ch ≡ 4840 sq yd ≡ 1⁄640 sq mi. International and US survey acre ≡ 4840 × 0.9144 × 0.9144 ≡ 4046.8564224 m².
Are is area unit, symbol: [a]. Definition of 1 are ≡ 100 m². The are area unit is equal to 100 square metres, used for measuring land area. It was defined by older forms of the metric system..
Barn is area unit, symbol: [b]. Definition of 1 barn ≡ 10^-28 m². Originally used in nuclear physics for expressing the cross sectional area of nuclei and nuclear reactions. .
Barony is area unit. Definition of 1 barony ≡ 4000 ac. ≡ 4000×4840×0.9144×0.9144 m².
Board is area unit, symbol: [bd]. Definition of 1 board ≡ 1 in × ft. ≡ 0.3048 × 0.0254 ≡ 7.74192×10^-3 m².
Circular inch is area unit, symbol: [circ in]. Definition of 1 circular inch ≡ π⁄4 sq in. Area of circle with diameter of 1 inch, value exactly π × 0.00016129 ≡ 5.067075×10^-4 m².
"<b>Circular mil
column10: circular thou is area unit, symbol: [circ mil]. Definition of 1 circular mil
column11: circular thou ≡  π⁄4 mil². Area of circle with diameter of 1 mil, value exactly π × 1.6129×10^-10 ≡ 5.067075×10^-10 m²."

@description: "<b>Circular mil
column10: circular thou is area unit, symbol: [circ mil]. Definition of 1 circular mil
column11: circular thou ≡  π⁄4 mil². Area of circle with diameter of 1 mil, value exactly π × 1.6129×10^-10 ≡ 5.067075×10^-10 m²."

@description: Cord is area unit. Definition of 1 cord ≡ 192 bd. ≡ 1.48644864 m².

Cuerda (PR Survey) is area unit, symbol: [cda]. Definition of 1 cuerda (PR Survey) ≡ 1 cda × cda ≡ 0.971 acre. Area unit used in some Spanish-speaking regions, also called Spanish acre ≡ 3930.395625 m².
Dunam is area unit. Definition of 1 dunam ≡ 1000 m². The new or metric dunam has been redefined as exactly one decare 1000 m².
Guntha (India) is area unit. Definition of 1 guntha (India) ≡ 121 sq yd. Most common used to measure the size of a piece of land ≡ 121 × 0.9144 × 0.9144 m².
Hectare is area unit, symbol: [ha]. Definition of 1 hectare ≡ 10000 m². Hectare is metric unit, primarily used in the measurement of land as a replacement for the imperial acre ≡ 10000 m².
Hide is area unit. Definition of 1 hide ≡ 120 ac (variable). The hide was an English unit of land measurement. Definition variable, ≡ 12 × ac ≡ 120 × 4046.8564224 m².
Rood is area unit, symbol: [ro]. Definition of 1 rood ≡ 1⁄4 ac. ≡ ac / 4 ≡ 4046.8564224 / 4 ≡ 1011.7141056 m².
Section is area unit. Definition of 1 section ≡ 1 mi × mi. Area equal with 1 mile by 1 mile square ≡ 1609.344² ≡ 2.589988110336×10^6^ m².
Shed is area unit. Definition of 1 shed ≡ 10^-52 m². Originally used in nuclear physics ≡ 10^-52 m².
Square centimetre is metric area unit, symbol: [cm²]. Definition of 1 square centimetre ≡ 1 cm × cm. Area equal with 1 centimetre by 1 centimetre square..
Square chain is area unit, symbol: [sq ch]. Definition of 1 square chain ≡ 66 ft × 66 ft ≡ 1⁄10 ac. ≡ (66 × 0.3048)² ≡ 404.68564224 m².
Square decimetre is metric area unit, symbol: [dm²]. Definition of 1 square decimetre ≡ 1 dm × dm. Area equal with 1 decimetre by 1 decimetre square..
Square foot is area unit, symbol: [sq ft]. Definition of 1 square foot ≡ 1 ft × ft. ≡ 0.3048 × 0.3048 ≡ 9.290304×10^-2 m².
Square inch is area unit, symbol: [sq in]. Definition of 1 square inch ≡ 1 in × in. Area equal with 1 inch by 1 inch square ≡ 0.0254 × 0.0254 ≡ 6.4516×10^-4 m².
Square kilometre is metric area unit, symbol: [km²]. Definition of 1 square kilometre ≡ 1km × 1km. .

Square link (Gunter's)(International) is area unit, symbol: [sq lnk]. Definition of 1 square link (Gunter's)(International) ≡ 1 lnk × lnk ≡ 0.66 ft × 0.66 ft. ≡ (0.66 × 0.3048 m)² ≡ 4.0468564224×10^-2 m².

Square link (Gunter's)(International) is area unit, symbol: [sq lnk]. Definition of 1 square link (Gunter's)(International) ≡ 1 lnk × lnk ≡ 0.66 ft × 0.66 ft. ≡ (0.66 × 0.3048 m)² ≡ 4.0468564224×10^-2 m².
Square link (Ramsden's) is area unit, symbol: [sq lnk]. Definition of 1 square link (Ramsden's) ≡ 1 lnk × lnk ≡ 1 ft × ft. ≡ 0.3048*0.3048 ≡ 0.09290304 m².
Square metre is metric area unit, symbol: [m²]. Definition of 1 square metre ≡ 1m × 1m. .
Square micrometre is metric area unit, symbol: [µm²]. Definition of 1 square micrometre ≡ 1 µm × µm. .

@description: Square mile is area unit, symbol: [sq mi]. Definition of 1 square mile ≡ 1 mi × mi. Area equal with 1 mile by 1 mile square ≡1609.344 × 1609.344 ≡ 2.589988110336×10^6 m².
Square millimetre is metric area unit, symbol: [mm²]. Definition of 1 square millimetre ≡ 1 mm × mm. .
Square nanometre is metric area unit, symbol: [nm²]. Definition of 1 square nanometre ≡ 1nm × 1nm. .
Square rod/pole/perch is area unit, symbol: [sq rd]. Definition of 1 square rod/pole/perch ≡ 1 rd × rd. Area equal with 1 rd by 1 rd square ≡ (0.3048 × 16.5)² ≡ 25.29285264 m².
Square (roofing) is area unit. Definition of 1 square (roofing) ≡ 10 ft × 10 ft. Area equal to 10 feet by 10 feet square ≡ (3.048 m)² ≡ 9.290304 m².
Square yard is area unit, symbol: [sq yd]. Definition of 1 square yard ≡ 1 yd × yd. Square yard (International) area is equal with 1 yard by 1 yard square ≡ 0.9144 × 0.9144 ≡ 0.83612736 m².
Stremma is area unit. Definition of 1 stremma ≡ 1000 m². The stremma is a Greek unit of land area, exactly ≡ 1000 m².

Township is area unit. Definition of 1 township ≡ 36 sq mi (US). Township area unit was used by the United States Public Land Survey System, refers to a square unit of land, that is nominally six (U.S. Survey) miles ≡36 × (6336000 / 3937)² ≡ 9.323994×10^7 m².
Yardland is area unit. Definition of 1 yardland ≡ 30 ac. yardland, yard of land or virgate was an English unit of land (primarily a measure of tax assessment) ≡ 1.2×10^5 m².
